   <talk_paragraph index="n025_trader_corin-noquest" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Corin$<BR>I wonder how brother Berlinin at Saint Haven is doing recently.<BR>* You need to receive a quest from Blacksmith Berlin.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n016_trader_borin-noquest" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>What you are looking at? Aren't you a spy sent by my older brother, are you?<BR>* You need to receive a quest from Blacksmith Berlin.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-noquest" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Dorin$<BR>You're suspicious! Is my younger brother Borin sending you to peep at my skills?<BR>* You need to receive a quest from Blacksmith Berlin.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-a" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What makes you worried?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Hmm, it's difficult.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-b" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>I finished making the music box but I need to empty my forge to attend Harori's fan meeting. As you know, if I empty here even for a day, something big would happen.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-c" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Why don't you ask someone to attend to your shop?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>I'm worried about my customers and the flame in the kiln could be blown out.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-d" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Mmm, that's good idea. It would be nice if there is a volunteer among my cousins. Can you ask around for me?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-acceptted" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>Accept Quest</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Get a substitute$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Please ask Corin at Calderock Village first. Calderock Village is not so far from here, he may do me a favour. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n025_trader_corin-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n025_trader_corin-2" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Talk about Berlin's request)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Corin$<BR>You are not buying anything. What do you wanna say?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n025_trader_corin-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Corin$<BR>Mmm, I'd like to grant Berlin's favour but it's been busy here, too. I heard Borin at Mana Ridge is free recently, why don't you ask Borin?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n016_trader_borin-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n016_trader_borin-2-a" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Oh, sorry. But I have to deliver the message.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>Don't ask anything if you don't buy!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n016_trader_borin-2-a" image="QN_BlackSmith_dorin.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n016_trader_borin-3" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Borin makes an awkward face after he'd gotten Blacksmith Berlin's message)</FONT><BR>Hmm. If it's as usual, it's no problem to care Berlin's forge. But I'm middle of making goods that Master Sorceress Cynthia ordered.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n016_trader_borin-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>Dorin would grant him a favour since his business is slack recently. Why don't you ask brother Dorin at Prairie Town?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-3-a" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Deliver Berlin's message)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Dorin$<BR>What's the matter? You don't seem that you came here to buy.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-3-d" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Corin said he's busy.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-3-b" mid="45" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Borin said Dorin would take it cause you are free.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Dorin$<BR>Well, that's difficult. What Corin or Borin said?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-3-c" mid="47" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Calm down!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Dorin$<BR>What?! Slack?!<BR>That bastard told you that?!<BR>I'm gonna go to Mana Ridge right now.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-3-d" mid="49" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What would you do about Berlin's request?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Dorin$<BR>How can I possibly calm down now?!<BR>I'll go to Mana Ridge and show him that I'm his older brother!<BR>How rude he is!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n002_trader_dorin-4" mid="51" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Dorin$<BR>Tsk, the business in Calderock Village seems to be thriving.<BR>Alright!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n002_trader_dorin-4" image="QN_BlackSmith_dorin.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Dorin$<BR>Tell Berlin, I can keep an eye on his kiln for a day. <BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Dorin shouts being unable to hold back his anger)</FONT><BR>Borin, bastard, you dare to dump it on me!!/html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-4-a" mid="56" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Dorin can keep an eye on your kiln for a day.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="55"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>So, what did my cousins say?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
